      "title": "Quota Action Notification",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has told Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe that he respects any decision taken at the party leaders' meeting, the Prime Minister's Office said.",
        "It is noteworthy that Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena has called for an emergency party leaders meeting at 4 pm today."
